      can lead to XSS attacks. Escape or avoid using it on user-controlled data like agent display names or descriptions.
      See <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.jenkins.io/doc/developer/security/xss-prevention/">Preventing Cross-Site Scripting in Jelly views</a>.
    </p>
  </s:sample>
